A beer barrel flatpack can be made at a workbench in the Workshop of a player-owned house with level 7 Construction, yielding 87 experience. The flatpack can be used on the Barrel space in the Kitchen. The player must have a hammer and a saw in their inventory to build it.

A '''beer barrel''' [[flatpack]] can be made at a [[workbench]] in the [[Workshop]] of a [[player-owned house]] with level 7 [[Construction]], yielding 87 [[experience]]. The flatpack can be used on the [[Barrel space]] in the [[Kitchen]]. The player must have a [[hammer]] and a [[saw]] in their inventory to build it.
